Everyone in Shouhua Academy

548
00:32:28,680 --> 00:32:30,460
is willing to fight

549
00:32:30,510 --> 00:32:31,510
for Jixing Abyss.

550
00:32:36,480 --> 00:32:38,220
All of you are too naive.

551
00:32:39,440 --> 00:32:41,570
The Emperor of Zhushui
has lived for centuries.

552
00:32:42,590 --> 00:32:44,730
Who knows how many tricks he has?

553
00:32:45,550 --> 00:32:47,140
If we fight them

554
00:32:48,200 --> 00:32:49,660
and lose,

555
00:32:50,790 --> 00:32:54,380
what will happen to Jixing Abyss?

556
00:32:55,110 --> 00:32:56,420
But no one can decide

557
00:32:57,030 --> 00:32:59,660
the fate of a person, a nation,

558
00:33:00,070 --> 00:33:01,290
or a world.

559
00:33:06,030 --> 00:33:07,710
To cower before the possibility of failure

560
00:33:08,400 --> 00:33:09,570
is to set ourselves up

561
00:33:09,830 --> 00:33:11,490
for failure.

562
00:33:12,200 --> 00:33:13,940
You'll think that failure is imminent.

563
00:33:14,960 --> 00:33:16,380
But that's cowardice.

564
00:33:17,590 --> 00:33:18,590
You don't

565
00:33:19,070 --> 00:33:20,290
surrender to your fate.

566
00:33:21,590 --> 00:33:22,590
You write

567
00:33:23,440 --> 00:33:24,980
your own fate.

568
00:33:30,350 --> 00:33:31,350
Indeed,

569
00:33:31,830 --> 00:33:34,330
the world needs young souls like you.

570
00:33:40,110 --> 00:33:44,490
I shall make it known that
Tianji will act on my behalf

571
00:33:45,110 --> 00:33:47,460
and lead the defense
against Zhushui Spiritual State.

572
00:33:48,270 --> 00:33:50,700
Everyone in Jixing Abyss shall unite.

573
00:33:51,350 --> 00:33:52,860
Invaders

574
00:33:53,440 --> 00:33:54,530
will not be spared.

575
00:34:01,640 --> 00:34:03,040
- Yes, Father.
- Yes, Your Majesty.

576
00:34:07,580 --> 00:34:10,300
[A cloud of pear blossoms
and a forlorn dream]

577
00:34:22,550 --> 00:34:23,550
Ming Yi.

578
00:34:23,660 --> 00:34:25,686
Are you all right?

579
00:34:25,710 --> 00:34:26,490
I'm fine.

580
00:34:26,590 --> 00:34:27,776
Immortal Situ isn't here.

581
00:34:27,800 --> 00:34:29,980
The spiritual power I
injected in you isn't helping.

582
00:34:34,320 --> 00:34:35,976
You can use your spiritual veins now,

583
00:34:36,000 --> 00:34:36,606
but that doesn't mean

584
00:34:36,630 --> 00:34:38,900
you should exhaust them for me.

585
00:34:39,590 --> 00:34:40,590
Don't worry.

586
00:34:40,800 --> 00:34:42,740
I still have a month to live.

587
00:34:44,190 --> 00:34:45,340
Touch wood!

588
00:34:45,800 --> 00:34:47,740
Don't give up, Ming Yi.

589
00:34:48,070 --> 00:34:50,050
We'll cure you within this month.

590
00:34:51,280 --> 00:34:52,280
- Don't worry.
- Ming Yi.

591
00:34:52,960 --> 00:34:55,260
- Ming Yi, are you all right?
- Master She.

592
00:34:56,230 --> 00:34:57,530
Please help Ming Yi.

593
00:34:59,880 --> 00:35:02,380
I'll brew more medicine.

594
00:35:14,880 --> 00:35:16,210
You never listen to me.

595
00:35:17,190 --> 00:35:18,780
Why must you leave?

596
00:35:19,000 --> 00:35:20,210
I only went out for a while.

597
00:35:20,510 --> 00:35:21,900
Are you trying to drive me crazy?

598
00:35:22,150 --> 00:35:23,566
Look at you now.

599
00:35:23,590 --> 00:35:25,166
You think you can head
to the Sunken Abyss alone?

600
00:35:25,190 --> 00:35:26,210
Not alone.

601
00:35:26,590 --> 00:35:28,530
I'm planning to bring you with me.

602
00:35:45,360 --> 00:35:47,490
Do not use your spiritual veins anymore.

603
00:35:48,590 --> 00:35:49,590
Otherwise,

604
00:35:50,190 --> 00:35:51,710
you won't live past the next few days.

605
00:35:54,880 --> 00:35:56,086
Therefore,

606
00:35:56,110 --> 00:35:58,780
I stayed up all night
to make this crossbow.

607
00:35:59,190 --> 00:36:01,336
Master, inject your power into it

608
00:36:01,360 --> 00:36:02,360
so that I can use it.

609
00:36:06,550 --> 00:36:07,606
No need to head to the Sunken Abyss.

610
00:36:07,630 --> 00:36:08,630
I'll go on your behalf.

611
00:36:09,480 --> 00:36:10,480
Master,

612
00:36:11,880 --> 00:36:13,170
we're going together.

613
00:36:13,590 --> 00:36:14,336
With you there,

614
00:36:14,360 --> 00:36:16,050
we'll breeze through the Sunken Abyss.

615
00:36:25,190 --> 00:36:26,190
You're done?

616
00:36:27,590 --> 00:36:28,980
- You're the death of me.
- Ow.

617
00:36:31,550 --> 00:36:32,980
It's filled to the brim.

618
00:36:43,550 --> 00:36:45,050
So this is the Sunken Abyss?

619
00:36:46,400 --> 00:36:48,300
It doesn't look so special.

620
00:36:51,550 --> 00:36:53,896
Why did Father pick this
place to raise netherbeasts

621
00:36:53,920 --> 00:36:54,920
back then?

622
00:36:56,070 --> 00:36:57,610
This place is full of miasma,

623
00:36:57,920 --> 00:37:00,040
perfect for harvesting and
storing Blood Pearl Bloom.

624
00:37:01,070 --> 00:37:02,860
Mu Qibai volunteered himself right then,

625
00:37:03,630 --> 00:37:04,376
so Father gave him

626
00:37:04,400 --> 00:37:06,050
a chance to serve.

627
00:37:06,590 --> 00:37:07,380
Father also said

628
00:37:07,550 --> 00:37:09,686
that once the Bo's medical classics
were taken out of the Sunken Abyss,

629
00:37:09,710 --> 00:37:10,896
the trap would be triggered.

630
00:37:10,920 --> 00:37:12,526
The Sunken Abyss would collapse right away,

631
00:37:12,550 --> 00:37:15,350
and the miasma would spread quickly
thanks to the Soul-Consuming Tree.

632
00:37:17,150 --> 00:37:18,256
Now that we don't need anything

633
00:37:18,280 --> 00:37:19,860
from Jixing Abyss anymore,

634
00:37:20,070 --> 00:37:21,650
why don't we give them

635
00:37:22,550 --> 00:37:24,260
a taste of miasma?

636
00:37:25,070 --> 00:37:26,070
Then

637
00:37:26,710 --> 00:37:28,776
allow me to stand guard next
to the Soul-Consuming Tree

638
00:37:28,800 --> 00:37:30,400
so that the tunnel will not be destroyed

639
00:37:30,920 --> 00:37:32,376
while you descend to get the classics.

640
00:37:32,400 --> 00:37:33,486
I see you find yourself

641
00:37:33,510 --> 00:37:34,980
a quick exit.

642
00:37:35,480 --> 00:37:38,210
It's only right to leave the important
task to you, my dear brother,

643
00:37:38,880 --> 00:37:40,840
so that you can take
credit for it before Father.

644
00:38:02,590 --> 00:38:04,380
Oh, the fiery phantom. Calm your mind

645
00:38:04,710 --> 00:38:05,710
as I retrieve this item.

646
00:38:06,550 --> 00:38:07,550
Break!

647
00:38:13,140 --> 00:38:14,780
[Bo's Medical Classics, Part 1]

648
00:38:27,510 --> 00:38:28,510
Where is he?

649
00:38:34,360 --> 00:38:35,360
Chao Yuan?

650
00:38:36,110 --> 00:38:38,070
Father asked me to
retrieve the medical classics.

651
00:38:38,920 --> 00:38:40,570
Are you here to help me

652
00:38:41,110 --> 00:38:42,820
or to steal it from me?

653
00:38:43,590 --> 00:38:44,590
Should I

654
00:38:45,000 --> 00:38:46,860
hand you over to Father

655
00:38:47,070 --> 00:38:48,070
or should I

656
00:38:50,000 --> 00:38:51,260
kill you right away?

657
00:39:03,150 --> 00:39:04,166
Situ Ling said

658
00:39:04,190 --> 00:39:05,816
he'd come here to retrieve
the medical classics.

659
00:39:05,840 --> 00:39:06,840
Where is he?

660
00:39:07,670 --> 00:39:08,690
It's my problem.

661
00:39:08,880 --> 00:39:10,300
I don't want to be indebted to him.

662
00:39:13,760 --> 00:39:15,900
Ming Yi, let's split up and search.

663
00:39:16,070 --> 00:39:17,070
Be careful, Master.

664
00:39:17,230 --> 00:39:18,230
You too.

665
00:39:22,590 --> 00:39:23,590
Break!

666
00:39:38,620 --> 00:39:40,540
[Bo's Medical Classics, Part 1]

667
00:39:46,940 --> 00:39:48,380
[Bo's Medical Classics, Part 1]

668
00:40:18,110 --> 00:40:19,110
My Lord,

669
00:40:19,280 --> 00:40:21,206
I have scouted the place
near Dragon Carp Terrace.

670
00:40:21,230 --> 00:40:22,490
There is no other entrance.

671
00:40:22,840 --> 00:40:25,320
Only the Soul-Consuming Tree
is connected to the Sunken Abyss.

672
00:40:26,000 --> 00:40:27,120
Tianji has already withdrawn

673
00:40:28,670 --> 00:40:30,340
all the guards from the Sunken Abyss.

674
00:40:32,030 --> 00:40:33,030
And now,

675
00:40:34,110 --> 00:40:35,820
we just need to seal the tree.

676
00:40:58,400 --> 00:40:59,400
What is this?

677
00:41:03,710 --> 00:41:04,710
I'm not sure.

678
00:41:07,440 --> 00:41:08,860
But since it's so well hidden,

679
00:41:09,590 --> 00:41:10,980
it must have a use.

680
00:41:11,920 --> 00:41:12,920
Keep it first.

681
00:41:14,190 --> 00:41:16,110
We'll see after we seal
the Soul-Consuming Tree.

682
00:41:33,590 --> 00:41:35,110
Something's afoot in the Sunken Abyss.

683
00:41:45,480 --> 00:41:46,300
An illusion.

684
00:41:46,480 --> 00:41:47,480
What are you looking for?

685
00:41:49,400 --> 00:41:50,400
Found you.

686
00:41:52,230 --> 00:41:53,530
A fairy like you

687
00:41:54,400 --> 00:41:56,560
trespassed into the Stoneheart
Cavern of Sunken Abyss.

688
00:41:56,630 --> 00:41:58,190
Are you here for Bo's medical classics?

689
00:41:59,230 --> 00:42:01,010
Who told you it's here?

690
00:42:01,920 --> 00:42:04,300
I'm here to sweep the floor.

691
00:42:31,800 --> 00:42:33,340
Oh, you! You're early.

692
00:42:34,840 --> 00:42:36,120
So this is the medical classics?

693
00:42:37,030 --> 00:42:37,610
Master She,

694
00:42:37,840 --> 00:42:39,570
the miasma is somehow spreading.

695
00:42:39,710 --> 00:42:40,896
We need to find Ming Yi as soon as possible

696
00:42:40,920 --> 00:42:41,570
and leave.

697
00:42:41,820 --> 00:42:42,606
You're right.

698
00:42:42,630 --> 00:42:43,630
Let's go.

699
00:42:45,360 --> 00:42:46,360
Sure.

700
00:42:46,590 --> 00:42:48,420
If you won't speak,

701
00:42:48,880 --> 00:42:51,010
I might just use Phantom Fire

702
00:42:52,030 --> 00:42:53,046
to give you

703
00:42:53,070 --> 00:42:56,570
the indelible brand of a criminal.

704
00:42:58,550 --> 00:43:00,010
Where should I brand you?

705
00:43:01,280 --> 00:43:02,280
Your chest

706
00:43:03,630 --> 00:43:05,780
or your pretty face?

707
00:43:07,800 --> 00:43:09,380
If you are disfigured...

708
00:43:16,000 --> 00:43:17,000
Where are you going?

709
00:43:19,190 --> 00:43:20,300
Run.

710
00:43:20,920 --> 00:43:21,920
Tell me.

711
00:43:22,030 --> 00:43:23,870
Who told you to look
for the medical classics?

712
00:43:36,230 --> 00:43:37,230
Please.

713
00:43:37,400 --> 00:43:38,646
Even on my last breath,

714
00:43:38,670 --> 00:43:39,816
I can kill a weakling like you

715
00:43:39,840 --> 00:43:41,050
easily.

716
00:43:48,920 --> 00:43:50,050
You think you can kill me?

717
00:44:04,320 --> 00:44:05,320
Go ahead.

718
00:44:06,030 --> 00:44:07,030
Kill me.

719
00:44:59,940 --> 00:45:03,140
♪ When the drifting clouds ♪

720
00:45:03,220 --> 00:45:05,540
♪ Flow toward me ♪

721
00:45:06,980 --> 00:45:09,780
♪ They drench my very soul ♪

722
00:45:09,820 --> 00:45:12,140
♪ Until it turns weak ♪

723
00:45:14,060 --> 00:45:16,820
♪ I deceive myself into
thinking that to love once ♪

724
00:45:16,860 --> 00:45:19,180
♪ Is enough ♪

725
00:45:20,500 --> 00:45:25,740
♪ Even if no true vow has ever been given ♪

726
00:45:27,580 --> 00:45:34,460
♪ From the stars, how long must
my tears travel to reach your heart? ♪

727
00:45:34,740 --> 00:45:41,060
♪ The tenderness you give me
is but love's poisonous wine ♪

728
00:45:42,020 --> 00:45:44,620
♪ I drink down all of my sorrow ♪

729
00:45:45,340 --> 00:45:48,620
♪ To trade for your freedom ♪

730
00:45:48,860 --> 00:45:54,580
♪ Once I've tasted love, I
long to be lost in its wine ♪

731
00:45:55,700 --> 00:46:02,380
♪ After long struggles in the
abyss, I ask the heavens ♪

732
00:46:02,780 --> 00:46:09,460
♪ Even if my armor shatters
for you, what does it matter? ♪

733
00:46:09,940 --> 00:46:13,220
♪ Fate is never wrong ♪

734
00:46:13,300 --> 00:46:16,700
♪ Even the sun must one day fall ♪

735
00:46:17,180 --> 00:46:24,020
♪ Against the world's absurdity,
I fight with all my might ♪

736
00:46:27,780 --> 00:46:34,596
♪ From the stars, how long must
my tears travel to reach your heart? ♪

737
00:46:34,620 --> 00:46:40,860
♪ The tenderness you give me
is but love's poisonous wine ♪

738
00:46:41,740 --> 00:46:44,340
♪ I drink down all of my sorrow ♪

739
00:46:45,100 --> 00:46:48,340
♪ To trade for your freedom ♪

740
00:46:48,580 --> 00:46:55,380
♪ Once I've tasted love, I
long to be lost in its wine ♪
